Job Details
A leading Busbar Trunking manufacturing company in Ras Al Khaimah is looking for a Female HR/Payroll/Accounts Assistant.
Location: Al Ghail Industrial Area, RAK
Interested candidates may forward their CV tojobs@powerbargulf.ae
Requirements
The candidate should have an Accounts background. Prior experience in Accounts, Payroll and Attendance Management will be an added advantage. Should possess excellent communication (English) skills. Should be well organized
